& [LambdaPhasorReferenceContributionSpecification] is a project-local finite math-processing contract
  + [source_snapshot_uuid] is 8c7262ec-3498-48f8-9d0a-844bd34a53da
  + [manifest_uuid] is 9832c73b-7c0f-4f34-a60f-b2955658024e
